"cs_corporation"

Mission Briefing: The whereabouts of a terrorist group that kidnapped four government officials last week have been disclosed by one of our informants. Enter the office building and secure the hostages or eliminate the terrorist threat entirely.

 Counter-Terrorists: Infiltrate the office building and rescue the remaining hostages from the Terrorists holding them.

Terrorists: Eliminate the Counter-Terrorist force before they rescue any hostages.

Other Notes: There are 4 hostages in this mission.
